{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act38side", "eventName": "揭幕者們", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "PV-8", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "無私鐵棘", "storyInfo": "知曉市政廳和法院動作的小威尼斯逼迫老威尼斯“退休”，決定趁狂歡節控制整座城市。明白了卡車互助會從未從家族陰影中脫身，伊雷妮決定組織司機們與家族做個了斷。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g7_reception", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=2>1100年11月8日    6:15 P.M.</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_only_medium", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1555_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老爺，您找我？", "name": "惶恐的家族成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1555_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1545_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安東有話問你。", "name": "老威尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1545_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡爾，這邊。", "name": "安東尼奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1544_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1555_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安東尼奧……", "name": "惶恐的家族成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1555_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最近新沃爾西尼還有車隊前往西西里城嗎？", "name": "安東尼奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1544_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1555_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "客運航線都在正常運轉。不過這段時間都是趕來新沃爾西尼參加狂歡節的，倒沒什麼人去外面。", "name": "惶恐的家族成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1555_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就好。", "name": "安東尼奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1544_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你現在去收拾行李，應該還來得及趕上末班車。", "name": "安東尼奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1544_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1555_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "惶恐的家族成員", "content": " 好的——"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "惶恐的家族成員", "content": " 啊、啊？安東尼奧，這是什麼意思？"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是還有個兄弟在西西里城嗎？如果不能繼續留在新沃爾西尼，也不能返回蒙特盧佩，你應該只能去投奔他吧。", "name": "安東尼奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1544_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為你的疏忽，我們丟了整整一車“輪胎”。", "name": "安東尼奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1544_1#4$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我給過你機會，但哪怕只是去港口迎接家主，你竟然也沒能辦好。薩盧佐家的老混蛋甚至在你之前找到了家主。", "name": "安東尼奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1544_1#8$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡爾，你還能活著離開，已經是我能給你的最體面的結局。拿著這個——", "name": "安東尼奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1544_1#8$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是一張銀行的本票，金額不小。"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "家族成員愣愣地接過來，他看見左上角寫著自己的名字，安東尼奧已經在上面畫了一個叉。"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安置費。沒了家族的庇佑，你要用錢的地方多得很。", "name": "安東尼奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1544_1#4$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1555_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在家族待了十幾年，在你來之前，我就一直跟著老爺，你不能當著老爺的面，對我——", "name": "惶恐的家族成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1555_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老爺，老爺——", "name": "惶恐的家族成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1555_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "員工犯了錯，自然要受到懲罰，您覺得呢？", "name": "安東尼奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1544_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1545_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，你是威尼斯載具公司的負責人。", "name": "老威尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1545_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1555_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1555_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-80,0", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "-80,0", "posto": "-280,0", "duration": 0.8, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 0.8, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1545_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1545_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……安東，這件事你並沒有提前知會我。", "name": "老威尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1555_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還請您不要怪罪。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "警察剛剛來過了。他們要檢查威尼斯旗下的載具工廠和檢修站，說是狂歡節前的例行檢查，但公函卻是臨時開具的。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛剛還收到了消息，阿爾貝托突然因為企業資格問題而被暫時拘留。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "毫無疑問，上午的庭審刺激了我們的拉維妮婭大法官，她希望以這種手段控制她所未知的局勢。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事情已經超出了我的控制，我不得不處置卡爾，否則很難服眾。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1545_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "老威尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1555_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一年，威尼斯載具公司謹遵《新都市管理法案》，唯一留下的把柄，也在昨天港口的那場火裡被燒掉了。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唯一一個可能影響到我們生意的人也處理了。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但等到狂歡節結束，拉維妮婭騰出手來，恐怕會盡全力針對我們。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1545_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你打算怎麼處理？", "name": "老威尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1555_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我本來的想法，是慢慢地改造這座城市——讓它既有其他城市所沒有的行之有效的法律，也有敘拉古人已經習以為常的地下秩序。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "威尼斯載具公司的生意做得這麼順遂，訣竅只有兩個：好好遵守《新都市管理法案》，不那麼遵守《新都市管理法案》。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其他家族顯然也在這麼做，不過適應新的遊戲規則是很難的。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "威尼斯家族本可以完美地融入這兩套秩序，我們已經做得很好了。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以時至今日，我們能做到拋棄其中的一部分，並轉而加速另一部分。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1545_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "老威尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1555_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想要，徹底控制這座城市？", "name": "老威尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1555_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1545_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你亂了陣腳，安東。別忘記，新沃爾西尼有西西里夫人的背書，她支持那群年輕人的改革。", "name": "老威尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1555_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這樣做，等於是在公開挑釁她的權威，與整個敘拉古作對。你在拿整個威尼斯家族打賭！", "name": "老威尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1555_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽起來是這樣。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1545_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上一個這麼做的，是貝納爾多……他才死了一年！", "name": "老威尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1555_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您害怕西西里夫人，害怕市政廳裡那些高喊理想的年輕人？", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……爸爸，您是真的老了。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1545_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "威尼斯是灰廳中最特別的存在，一個幾乎由“雜種”組成的家族，沒有血緣關係的離群魯珀、英格麗那樣的沃爾珀、你這樣的佩洛……", "name": "老威尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1555_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其他家族並沒有多麼看得起我們，但我們走到了今天。這裡面凝聚了每一個威尼斯人的心血。", "name": "老威尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1555_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的聯繫比血緣更緊密，我希望家裡的每個人都能有體面的結局。", "name": "老威尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1555_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而你想要將家族置於如此險境……安東，你似乎遺忘了我的教誨。", "name": "老威尼斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1555_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爸爸，我是不是從來沒講過，我這隻佩洛，是怎麼來到敘拉古的？", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1545_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "老威尼斯"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我是個軍人，隸屬“真正玻利瓦爾人解放運動”。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1545_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我對玻利瓦爾的局勢，只有一些很粗淺的瞭解……", "name": "老威尼斯"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實在玻利瓦爾，為誰當兵都沒有任何區別，你不用懂三方勢力為什麼打仗，反正我們這些人不過是靠賣命討一條活路。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我所在的游擊隊在掃蕩辛嘉斯王朝的一個村鎮時暴露了行蹤，整支隊伍都成了俘虜。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們這二十個人掏乾淨了身上的每一個口袋，湊了所有家當買通行刑官，求他把我們在名單上的身分從“死刑犯”改成了“勞役犯”。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "負責轉運我們的上級官員是個大腹便便的貴族，他那天喝醉了酒，弄錯了審查流程，只開來了一輛卡車……只夠坐十個人。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行刑官質問他怎麼辦，您知道那個傢伙是什麼反應嗎？", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1545_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "老威尼斯"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他一邊打著酒嗝，一邊掏出筆在我們的名單上隨手畫了一個圈，說：“名單上明明只有這十個人，不是嗎？”", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們殺了他，割下了他的腦袋，逃離了玻利瓦爾，再後來的事情，您就知道了。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1545_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安東，你從來沒有提過——", "name": "老威尼斯"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太久了，哈哈，久到我幾乎忘了。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您知道我重新想起來這件事，是因為什麼嗎？", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我去找年輕有為的市長大人商討新沃爾西尼的物流建設，他在拒絕我後，向我分享了這座新城市的由來和使命……", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所謂的“試驗場”，將舊的人放進來，再用與敘拉古傳統迥異的新秩序去管理它……", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們知道必然會有人反抗，會有不可調和的矛盾，甚至會有一群又一群人在這個過程中被吞沒……但是為了可能的未來，無所謂。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而這一切，都只是因為四個年輕人坐在了灰廳的圓桌前，進行了一番慷慨激昂的遊說……", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "西西里夫人便大手一揮，從敘拉古二十三座移動城市裡撥了一座給他們……", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "輕率得就像當時那個貴族隨手在我們的名字上畫了一個圈。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爸爸，萊昂圖索當時講得很真誠，也很振奮，我卻差點按捺不住地想笑出聲……這個年輕的傻小子什麼都不懂。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您剛剛說，我亂了陣腳？", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不是的，我要做的事情，從來都沒有變過。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我討厭那個貴族，討厭西西里夫人，我討厭他們隨手畫圈的權力，我要把這一切，從他們手中奪過來！", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1545_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安東……", "name": "老威尼斯"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼——好了爸爸，我說得有點多了。我今天不是來聽您教誨什麼是體面，也不是來分析敘拉古的局勢的。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "單憑我這一年的運作，還不足以讓我們坐上賭桌……", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爸爸，家裡有一艘陸行艦正在離此不遠的航線上吧？我想要它的緊急調度權。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而這，是家主才能做到的事情。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1545_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要是不答應，守在門外的那些人，大概會像對付卡爾那樣對付我？", "name": "老威尼斯"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那倒是不會，您是個真正的體面人。", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1545_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "老威尼斯"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1544_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爸爸，您老了。您不是一直把退休掛在嘴邊嗎？", "name": "安東尼奧"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "56_g9_truckcamp", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請問，伊雷妮不在營地嗎？", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……大、大法官女士？", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃、呃，伊雷妮不在。大家為了祝賀伊雷妮無罪釋放，去慶祝了。", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你為什麼沒有去？", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我、您看，我不是還在維修這些卡車嗎？", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明天就是狂歡節了，多的是用車的地方……", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總得有人來保養吧。", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在撒謊，先生。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "見到伊雷妮之後，麻煩告訴她，我需要見她，隨時都可以。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……好。", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1550_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "56_g11_newvolsiniipier", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$escape_intro", "key": "$escape_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1561_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊雷妮，來，這一年的排班表。", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1561_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按照你說的，我把和威尼斯載具公司有關的記錄都標記了出來，每一趟出車的時間、載貨說明、司機的名字……都在上面。", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1561_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，和索默爾筆記本上寫的都對得上。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "索默爾要接小古莉來新沃爾西尼；卡米洛一直偷偷靠酒精壓制傷病，不得不求助互助會之外的人；吉安和魯傑羅也各有各的難處……", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每一個被盯上的成員，都是他們精挑細選過的。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出車記錄不算多，但頻率很穩定，那天晚上絕對不是他們第一次偷運武器進城……", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊雷妮，你沒猜錯，那個法官的確去營地找了你。她走後，後面還有幾個家族的成員鬼鬼祟祟跟著她。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那……", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#6$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一直開車跟在後面，看她走進了法院才回來。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就好。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有一件事。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#3$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我正好看見薩盧佐酒業的法務團隊急匆匆地進了法院。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我打聽了一下，就在不久前，警察毫無預兆地去了薩盧佐的酒莊，帶走了阿爾貝托。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同時被找上的，還有威尼斯載具公司。現在警察和法官應該在對他們的工廠進行臨檢。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉維妮婭應該還不知道武器的事，但車禍和港口失火傳遞出來的訊號已經很危險……", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#4$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊昂圖索受了傷，至今還在醫院，她作為新沃爾西尼的大法官，只能想盡辦法控制局勢。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#4$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她沒有直接對卡車互助會採用同樣的手段……她是來警告我們的。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者說，最後通牒。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1561_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，那柳德米拉剛剛說的……", "name": "卡車司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1561_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管是阿爾貝托，還是小威尼斯，都不可能坐以待斃。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉維妮婭現在很危險。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些傢伙只是跟在法官的身後，並沒有動手的意思。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#1$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡畢竟是新沃爾西尼，警察還在街道上巡邏呢。而且，不是有一個現成的更好的時機嗎？", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是說，狂歡節……", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#5$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們可以去提醒那個法官。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#5$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊雷妮沒有動，良久，她搖了搖頭。"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還是不想讓她知道互助會的事情，但你真的能眼睜睜看著她出事嗎？", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#5$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少，她人不壞。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#5$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你誤會了，柳德米拉。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#5$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們如今想要置身事外已經來不及了。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果那些家族敢在狂歡節上直接對拉維妮婭動手，那他們更加不會放過卡車互助會。到時候，我們只能任他們宰割。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是在想到底應該怎麼做。我不想再看到像索默爾那樣……", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#6$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直接告訴拉維妮婭，並不是最好的選擇。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#4$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "柳德米拉，你見過那批武器？有多少？", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按照那個量和排班表上的總記錄來估算——", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#7$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "威尼斯在城內的武器大概夠武裝幾個戰術小隊，幾十個人。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#7$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們光登記在冊的正式成員就有兩百多人，算上那些臨時工和約聘人員的話，人數還會更多。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我突然意識到，卡車互助會其實是整個新沃爾西尼規模最大的組織。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果只是暗中保護一個人的話，或許還是做得到的。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你真的只是想要保護那個法官嗎？", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#6$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "索默爾至少教會了我一件事，那就是除了我們自己，這座城市裡的任何人都不值得信任。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只能靠自己保護自己……哪怕那意味著暴力。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#8$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#6$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在烏薩斯的時候，我認識一個有類似想法的人。她最後迷失了自我。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#2$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想阻攔我？", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……索默爾的事情需要有一個結局。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#3$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但顯然，他也不會願意看到那樣的你。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#3$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1502_crosly_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊雷妮，我會確保你不會越過最後那條線……", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1502_crosly_1#7$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我答應你，柳德米拉。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很清楚自己在做什麼。", "name": "伊雷妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1542_1#2$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}